    "body": "Yep (although RPC port and hostname are configurable, we using default ones - and once TLS is released, the only thing that will be changed is that `localhost:8545` will encrypt its communication, and expect client to communicate using TLS).\r\n\r\nI will also expose ability to provide certificate and private key files, therefore, if you can make sure that WebView works with a given certificate/key, then you start Geth node with those certificate/key - and we should be ok.",
